            <h3>4.1 Rental Obligations</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Inspect bike before accepting</li>
                <li>Use bike responsibly and legally</li>
                <li>Return bike on time and in same condition</li>
                <li>Report any damage immediately</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>4.2 Prohibited Uses</h3>
            <p>Renters may not:</p>
